{
  "stem": "7437.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To this day, when I walk and I see somebody walking in front of me who's very tall and reminds me of the build of my father-- and my mother was also almost six foot tall-- when I see people that remind me of my father and mother, I have to run in front and look in their faces to convince myself that it's not them.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SIGH] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know how to express my feelings now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the beginning, it was rage, anger, and hate, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, I don't know what I would do if I would meet, person-to-person, the human being who murdered my father or my mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know if I am capable of avenging their death with, with the death of the perpetrator.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I cannot forgive, not yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when I came to my hometown and I found not-- nobody, I went back to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were other survivors like me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we tried to comfort each other and see what else we could do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, at that time, people kept telling us, whoever survived is now in Germany, because everybody was concentrating in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By that time, I guess the war was over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we decided, we have to make our way to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so a group of us did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was an, an illegal way of doing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went from our place, from our town, Horochow, back to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From Lutsk, we went to Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's in, in, in Czechoslovakia at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From Bratislava, we made our way to Vienna, Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from Vienna, we ended up in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
